<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <meta name="description" content="A minimal event marketing project">
    <title><%= title %> | DryBar Comics</title>

    <!-- fonts -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Source+Code+Pro:wght@500&family=Spartan:wght@500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- icons -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.7.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css" />

    <!-- styles -->
    <link type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
</head>
<body>
<div class="global-wrap">
    <div class="global-content">
        <!-- start:: header -->
        <%- include('partials/header.ejs') %>
        <!-- end:: header -->

        <!-- start:: main -->
        <main class="global-main">
            <div class="post-section">
                <div class="post-header item is-hero is-page is-first post no-image page">
                    <div class="item-container global-color">
                        <div class="item-content">
                            <h1 class="item-title">FAQ</h1>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="post-content">
                <h3 id="general-features">1. Our Price Guarantee (Accommodation)</h3>

                <p lang="answer">Our in-house team work
                    tirelessly to curate a unique
                    selection of accommodation options for
                    each individual festival, based on location,
                    price, convenience and that je ne sais quoi.
                </p>

                <h3 id="general-features">2. Event is cancelled - Where is my refund</h3>

                <p lang="answer">
                    For each event,
                    customers will have been emailed directly to
                    explain the next course of action for the event you
                    have booked, you do not need to do anything.
                    Please note we aim to contact you prior to the event where possible,
                    please check your junk and spam.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- start:: icon -->
            <%- include('partials/icon.ejs') %>
            <!-- end:: icon -->
        </main>
        <!-- end:: main -->

        <!-- start:: footer -->
        <%- include('partials/footer.ejs') %>
        <!-- end:: footer -->
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>

